        <title>[LO 1.1; LO 1.2; LO 2.1; LO 2.2]</title>
        <para id="id9999952">Your teacher will arrange a visit to a suitable garden in your neighbourhood, or perhaps just to a part of your school grounds. It must be an area where the gardener does not work every day. </para>
        <list id="id21681549" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Why is that so? </item>
